data.description: *HIDDEN TREASURE* This property boasts a LARGE .3 acre parcel backing to a greenbelt with room to grow a HUGE garden or simply enjoy the gorgeous sunrise with unobstructed views while you drink your morning coffee. There is plenty of room to develop an RV access area from the front of the home and an existing rear yard gate access from the greenbelt. This home has luxury vinyl flooring throughout, an open kitchen with large breakfast bar, lots of natural light, a large primary suite with walk-in closet and a high-efficiency wood burning fireplace. This home is conveniently located near schools and is within walking distance to Cameron Park Lake and shopping. Great starter home for a young family!
